metadata.description:
The world's first NFT game. The game was developed with JavaScript, Python and PDF technologies. Your goal is to catch all falling red blocks. Don't miss the moment! There is no loss in this game. The fact of missing the moment and completing the game is assessed solely by the player. Not all moments in life are worthy not to be missed.

 

Control:

Use mouse over the entire document.

 

Challenge:

Take part in the challenge! Publish your results with the hashtag #CatchMometChallenge.

 

The game works fine in:  

  • Google Chrome v.91.0.4472.114  
  • Microsoft Edge v.91.0.864.54  
  • Opera v.77.0.4054.90

Don't forget to enable JavaScript.
